Trump names his son-in-law a
senior White

00:11.345 --> 00:14.882 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
House adviser, sparking concerns
of nepotism.

00:14.915 --> 00:20.754 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
