adviser Kellyanne
Conway about how this and why
some Cabinet

00:20.787 --> 00:24.091 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
nominees have incomplete
background checks.

00:24.124 --> 00:29.496 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Also ahead, a look at President
Obama's health
care legacy, the biggest and
most controversial

00:29.529 --> 00:32.266 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
