applies to White
House jobs.

02:34.287 --> 02:39.459 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Today, Kushner's lawyer argues
it doesn't
and said Kushner won't be taking
a salary.

02:39.493 --> 02:44.064 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
As for Kushner's business
holdings, a senior
transition official said he will
resign as

02:44.097 --> 02:50.437 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
CEO and divest from a
significant number of
assets, including foreign
investments.

02:50.470 --> 02:52.606 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour," I'm John
Yang.

02:52.639 --> 02:56.977 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
