pushed back
against a U.S. intelligence
report that it

03:03.316 --> 03:05.585 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
meddled in the presidential
campaign.

03:05.619 --> 03:10.290 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
