President Vladimir
Putin personally ordered the
effort.

03:10.323 --> 03:16.396 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Today, a Kremlin spokesman said
the investigation
is "reminiscent of a
witch-hunt," echoing

03:16.430 --> 03:19.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
