Trump used last
week.

03:19.599 --> 03:24.638 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN (through translator): We
still don't know
what data those who make such
unfounded accusations

03:24.671 --> 03:26.506 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
have.

03:26.540 --> 03:30.077 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We still strongly reject any
involvement of
Moscow and accusations that
Russian officials

03:30.110 --> 03:33.213 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
or institutions were involved in
any hacker
attacks.

03:33.246 --> 03:36.650 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We are observing a serious
fatigue with these
accusations.

03:36.683 --> 03:40.954 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Mr. Trump today
deflected questions
today about the hacking.

03:40.987 --> 03:44.091 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He said -- quote -- "We will
talk to you about
that at another time."

03:44.124 --> 03:49.362 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He holds his news conference
since the election
on Wednesday.

03:49.396 --> 03:54.634 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
China warned president-elect
Donald Trump
today that it will "take
revenge" if he reneges

03:54.668 --> 03:57.571 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
on the so-called one China
policy.

03:57.604 --> 04:00.740 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
