part of China.

04:00.774 --> 04:06.313 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
The threat from Chinese
state-run media came
after the Taiwanese president
made a weekend

04:06.346 --> 04:10.951 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
stopover in Houston, Texas, and
met with Republican
lawmakers.

04:10.984 --> 04:15.856 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Mr. Trump has spoken with the
Taiwanese leader,
and at one point, appeared to
suggest that

04:15.889 --> 04:19.593 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the one-China policy might need
reconsidering.

04:19.626 --> 04:24.197 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The man accused of killing five
people at
the Fort Lauderdale, Florida,
airport had

04:24.231 --> 04:27.067 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
his first appearance in federal
court today.

04:27.100 --> 04:33.240 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
According to court documents,
Esteban Santiago
has admitted to the fatal
shooting last Friday.

04:33.273 --> 04:38.178 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
At the hearing today, the Iraq
War veteran
said he understood the charges
against him,

04:38.211 --> 04:40.914 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
which carry the death penalty.

04:40.947 --> 04:46.019 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
