04:47.821 --> 04:53.293 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A powerful storm system moved in
over the
weekend, unleashing heavy
downpours and strong

04:53.326 --> 04:55.095 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
winds.

04:55.128 --> 05:00.567 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
