residents in Reno,
Nevada, to evacuate after the
Truckee River

05:00.600 --> 05:02.335 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
overflowed.

05:02.369 --> 05:07.941 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The storm also blew down a giant
California
sequoia that is famed for a
tunnel carved

05:07.974 --> 05:09.276 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
into its truck.

05:09.309 --> 05:11.978 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It had stood for centuries.

05:12.012 --> 05:16.950 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The musical "La La Land" swept
seven Golden
Globe film awards.

05:16.983 --> 05:21.321 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the ceremony also touched
off a war of
words with president-elect
Trump.

05:21.354 --> 05:27.227 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It started with actress Meryl
Streep and her
speech accepting a lifetime
achievement award.

05:27.260 --> 05:32.432 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
