imitating a disabled
reporter during the primaries.

05:32.465 --> 05:40.307 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MERYL STREEP, Actress: And this
instinct to
humiliate, when it's modeled by
someone in

05:40.340 --> 05:45.712 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the public platform, by someone
powerful,
it filters down into everybody's
life, because

05:45.745 --> 05:49.916 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
it kind of gives permission for
other people
to do the same thing.

05:49.950 --> 05:54.387 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
When the powerful use their
position to bully
others, we all lose.

05:54.421 --> 05:57.757 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The
president-elect fired back
on Twitter today.

05:57.791 --> 06:02.996 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He called Streep -- quote --
"one of the most
overrated actresses in
Hollywood" and -- quote

06:03.029 --> 06:06.366 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
-- "a Hillary flunky who lost
big."

06:06.399 --> 06:12.839 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Mr. Trump also tweeted praise
for Fiat Chrysler's
decision to build new jeeps and
a truck in

06:12.872 --> 06:15.775 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the Midwestern U.S., instead of
Mexico.

06:15.809 --> 06:18.144 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The company said it's creating
2,000 jobs.

06:18.178 --> 06:22.782 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
On Wall Street, meanwhile,
stocks followed
oil prices lower.

06:22.816 --> 06:27.320 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Dow Jones industrial average
lost 76 points
to close at 19887.

06:27.354 --> 06:34.027 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Nasdaq rose 10 points, and
the S&amp;P 500
slipped eight.

06:34.060 --> 06:39.099 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
