a packed week
for the president-elect; a look
at the legacy

06:44.704 --> 06:59.619 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of President Obama's health care
overhaul;
and much more.

06:59.653 --> 07:05.592 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
