on day one.

07:43.496 --> 07:47.400 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: All this ahead
of a packed
week, with two confirmation
hearings set for

07:47.434 --> 07:52.972 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
