leader, Chuck
Schumer, called it a rush job.

08:04.551 --> 08:06.386 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

08:06.419 --> 08:08.655 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHUCK SCHUMER (D-NY), Minority
Leader: Jamming
all these hearings into one or
two days, making

08:08.688 --> 08:13.126 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
