it.

08:20.767 --> 08:24.404 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Schumer has
threatened to
slow down the Senate
confirmation process

08:24.437 --> 08:27.907 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
