is that President
Obama's nominees all cleared
their ethics

08:52.966 --> 08:56.669 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
review process before their
hearings, even
before they were announced.

08:56.703 --> 09:01.107 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Office of Government Ethics
says some
Trump nominees have not even
filed their paperwork

09:01.141 --> 09:02.809 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
yet.

09:02.842 --> 09:05.645 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
