you for that
report, but take us through this
process.

09:05.678 --> 09:07.514 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
What exactly is required of
these nominees?

09:07.547 --> 09:10.383 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Well, it
depends on what
committee you're going in front
of.

09:10.417 --> 09:14.053 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
