committee of
choice -- or the committee that
oversees their

09:22.429 --> 09:24.764 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
nomination, and they have to
fill out a committee
questionnaire.

09:24.798 --> 09:30.203 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, Judy, what depends on each
committee
is the following, whether or not
an ethics

09:30.236 --> 09:33.373 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
review must be filed before a
hearing or simply
before a vote.

09:33.406 --> 09:35.175 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
