require tax forms
from the past.

09:43.450 --> 09:47.287 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Tell us a little
more about
what is missing for some of
these nominees.

09:47.320 --> 09:50.890 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: These ethics
forms that we're
talking about are significant.

09:50.924 --> 09:52.792 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
