in the 40
years has a nominee gone before
a hearing

10:35.535 --> 10:37.737 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
without having their ethics
review completed.

10:37.770 --> 10:39.472 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Is that your understanding?

