provisions
by making the Medicaid expansion
optional

30:16.782 --> 30:19.117 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
for states.

30:19.151 --> 30:23.855 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Senator Charles Grassley, a
Republican from
Iowa who was involved in the
initial bipartisan

30:23.889 --> 30:29.061 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
