and felt they
had a mandate, decided to move
forward alone.

30:33.865 --> 30:35.567 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

30:35.600 --> 30:37.736 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLES GRASSLEY (R), Iowa: It
was a take
it or leave it, and so,
basically, we were

30:37.769 --> 30:39.571 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
