things that
happened going wrong.

30:50.749 --> 30:56.321 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think it's a perfect example
of trying to
do something in a partisan way.

30:56.354 --> 31:00.992 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
SARAH VARNEY: The Obama
administration believed
the law would eventually become
popular as

31:01.026 --> 31:03.395 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
