benefits.

31:03.428 --> 31:08.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But public opinion remained
divided.

31:08.300 --> 31:13.105 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Republicans voted to repeal or
delay part
or all of it more than 60 times,
always facing

31:13.138 --> 31:18.110 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the prospect of a certain veto
from President
Obama.

31:18.143 --> 31:21.613 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Now president-elect Donald Trump
has vowed
to kill the law for good.

31:21.646 --> 31:26.151 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
DONALD TRUMP (R),
President-Elect: Repealing
Obamacare is one of the single
most important

31:26.184 --> 31:28.687 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
