8.

31:28.720 --> 31:31.623 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: A promise that
appealed to many
voters around the country.

31:31.656 --> 31:37.763 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Here in Mansfield, Ohio, once a
booming manufacturing
town, the Affordable Care Act
has brought

31:37.796 --> 31:42.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
