care jobs and
an influx of federal money.

31:42.234 --> 31:46.605 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
All told, nearly one million
Ohioans are covered
under Obamacare.

31:46.638 --> 31:50.675 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But economic angst in Rust Belt
states like
this one handed the presidential
election

31:50.709 --> 31:55.981 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to Donald Trump, giving him the
power to repeal
President Obama's signature
domestic policy.

31:56.014 --> 31:58.483 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KARI WESTFIELD, Third Street
Family Health
Services: This area was, the
kids would get

31:58.517 --> 32:00.919 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
