and not come
back.

32:00.952 --> 32:03.855 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: What happens next
is up for
grabs.

32:03.889 --> 32:08.827 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Kari Westfield helps sign
patients up for
Medicaid in this Ohio county
where Mr. Trump

32:08.860 --> 32:10.829 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
won nearly 70 percent of the
vote.

32:10.862 --> 32:16.535 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KARI WESTFIELD: The most recent
was the GM
closing, and that was a huge,
huge hit to

32:16.568 --> 32:18.336 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
