32:18.370 --> 32:22.040 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: As manufacturing
plants here
have closed, nearly 30 percent
of residents

32:22.073 --> 32:26.912 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
have had to enroll in Medicaid,
which was
expanded in Ohio to include most
low-income

32:26.945 --> 32:29.681 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
adults under the Affordable Care
Act.

32:29.714 --> 32:34.986 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Since the health law took
effect, the share
of uninsured patients at Third
Street Family

32:35.020 --> 32:42.427 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Health Services, where Westfield
works, fell
from 30 percent to 10 percent.

32:42.460 --> 32:47.766 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That includes Larry Avery, a
31-year-old basketball
coach who has been rushing to
get medical

32:47.799 --> 32:50.368 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
