takes the
law away.

32:50.402 --> 32:53.705 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LARRY AVERY, Patient: I just
thought it was
just a move that he was doing
just to make

32:53.738 --> 32:59.511 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
it harder than what it already
is, because,
I mean, if it's working, if it
helps, why

32:59.544 --> 33:00.879 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
would you want to take that
away?

33:00.912 --> 33:04.683 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I don't think it benefits the
country at all.

33:04.716 --> 33:08.920 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Among those trying
to enroll
in Obamacare's expanded Medicaid
are Trump

33:08.954 --> 33:10.922 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
supporters Mary and Jim Heenan.

33:10.956 --> 33:16.228 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A nurse trying to recover from
an opioid addiction,
Mary Heenan says she and her
husband need

33:16.261 --> 33:17.996 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
help.

33:18.029 --> 33:22.033 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And though she says it can be
difficult to
reconcile, Heenan still despises
the health

33:22.067 --> 33:23.768 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
law.

33:23.802 --> 33:27.305 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
She says it forced the surgeons
she once worked
with to provide shoddy medical
care.

33:27.339 --> 33:31.209 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARY HEENAN, Patient: I know I'm
in this spot
where I need help right now from
the government,

33:31.243 --> 33:38.483 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
but the Affordable Care Act is
the worst thing
that's ever happened to this
country.

33:38.516 --> 33:43.755 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that's exactly why I voted
for Trump,
because I knew Hillary was going
to follow

33:43.788 --> 33:45.590 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
