33:54.232 --> 33:57.369 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JOHN CORLETT, Center for
Community Solutions:
I think people have a natural
inclination

33:57.402 --> 34:01.573 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
