starts, that
it's hard to stop,that it's hard
to take down.

34:01.606 --> 34:04.876 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think a lot of people sort
of approached
it that way, said, well, no,
they wouldn't

34:04.910 --> 34:06.645 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
do that.

34:06.678 --> 34:09.414 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Across Ohio, the
health law
has dramatically reduced the
number of people

34:09.447 --> 34:11.516 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
