34:11.549 --> 34:16.588 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
At MetroHealth in Cleveland as
elsewhere in
the country, the influx of
insured patients

34:16.621 --> 34:21.960 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
has allowed the health system to
provide more
preventive care and cut costs by
nearly 30

34:21.993 --> 34:23.828 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
percent.

34:23.862 --> 34:27.999 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Despite strong opinions about
what's become
known as Obamacare, elements of
the law remain

34:28.033 --> 34:29.768 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
