until age
26.

34:36.908 --> 34:39.244 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
PROTESTERS: No repeal without
replace.

34:39.277 --> 34:43.949 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Mindy Hedges
showed up at a
rally outside Senator Rob
Portman's office

34:43.982 --> 34:48.687 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in Columbus to show how vital
the law has
been for those with medical
problems.

34:48.720 --> 34:50.922 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MINDY HEDGES, Ohio: I'm scared
for our country.

34:50.956 --> 34:52.824 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I'm scared for a lot of reasons.

34:52.857 --> 34:55.593 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Before the health
law, she couldn't
get insurance.

34:55.627 --> 34:59.831 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MINDY HEDGES: I was so grateful
to President
Obama.

34:59.864 --> 35:03.501 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I owe President Obama my life.

35:03.535 --> 35:08.139 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
