into any consideration.

35:12.177 --> 35:14.145 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And my age, they couldn't take
into consideration.

35:14.179 --> 35:18.283 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Hedges has been
calling her
congressman and senators every
day to make

35:18.316 --> 35:20.018 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
sure they hear her story.

35:20.051 --> 35:25.957 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MINDY HEDGES: Will he be
supporting keeping
it at least until we have
something better

35:25.991 --> 35:29.561 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
