substitute for it?

35:29.594 --> 35:35.467 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: But there are
others, especially
small business owners and the
self-employed,

35:35.500 --> 35:38.536 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
