36:04.029 --> 36:08.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Those frustrations
drove Hamper
to vote for Mr. Trump, who says
he wants to

36:08.867 --> 36:14.172 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
keep the law's more popular
provisions and
scrap the rest in favor of a
less regulated

36:14.205 --> 36:16.107 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
insurance market.

36:16.141 --> 36:20.145 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
