But Hamper says the law has
already done enough
damage.

36:32.690 --> 36:35.060 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ANIETRA HAMPER: This isn't
working.

36:35.093 --> 36:43.802 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
