more affordability,
OK.

36:49.841 --> 36:54.813 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And like every other American,
you know, we
have to hope that that's what we
get.

36:54.846 --> 36:59.084 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
