that it takes
a period of time to get total
replacement,

37:11.329 --> 37:16.534 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
or whether it's done
incrementally, those
decisions have not been made at
this point.

37:16.568 --> 37:21.639 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: Whatever the
outcome, many observers
say President Obama's legacy
will forever

37:21.673 --> 37:26.311 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
