solve one
of the nation's most intractable
problems.

37:26.344 --> 37:30.915 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BOB KOCHER: I think, forever, we
have changed
the conversation that we need to
have an approach

37:30.949 --> 37:32.784 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to cover all Americans.

37:32.817 --> 37:38.490 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, if nothing else, this law
now leads Republicans
to agree that we need to have an
approach

37:38.523 --> 37:40.391 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
