high-quality insurance.

37:40.425 --> 37:44.095 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
So I think that's a real
accomplishment, and
that wouldn't have happened
without this law.

37:44.129 --> 37:49.400 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JONATHAN OBERLANDER: Some of the
most gifted
presidents in the 20th century
tried comprehensive

37:49.434 --> 37:51.369 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
health care reform, and they
failed.

37:51.402 --> 37:53.605 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
President Obama succeeded.

37:53.638 --> 37:55.607 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
This is not a footnote in
history.

37:55.640 --> 37:57.976 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It will go down as a landmark.

37:58.009 --> 38:02.180 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SARAH VARNEY: And one of the
most important
legacies of the Obama years.

38:02.213 --> 38:06.618 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour" and
Kaiser Health News,
