a visit.

48:44.188 --> 48:46.390 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
CRISTINA QUINN: It's 5:30 a.m.

48:46.423 --> 48:48.092 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
