week outside
of the Hope House Rehab Center
in Roxbury.

49:01.005 --> 49:04.875 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The group is made up of guys
from various
homeless shelters and recovery
programs around

49:04.909 --> 49:06.243 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
